# Large binary artifacts — keep local (and OneDrive-synced), don't commit to git.
# Project archives (source data + generated test projects) are 40–130 MB each.
*.c4p
# ...except the tiny blank-project SEED shipped as package data (Project.new()).
!c4proj/templates/blank.c4p
# Project JSON exports (`c4proj export`) — REAL client project data: room/device names, IP
# addresses. This repo is PUBLIC; never commit these.
exports/
*.export.json
# Raw packet captures from the protocol recon.
*.pcap
# The controller log snapshot (hundreds of files, large).
research/log_snapshot/
